OL,3,CBusinesses say they've lost hundreds
OL,4,Cof thousands of pounds because of
OL,5,Croadworks
OL,7,FBusiness owners in Oxford say they
OL,8,Fhave been left hundreds of thousands
OL,9,Fof pounds out of pocket because of
OL,10,Fongoing roadworks, and have been
OL,11,Frefused compensation by Network Rail.
OL,13,FThe Botley Road has been closed since
OL,14,FApril 2023 as part of a #231 million
OL,15,Fupgrade of Oxford railway station.
OL,17,FIt was originally meant to reopen in
OL,18,FOctober last year, but that has been
OL,19,Fdelayed until next summer.
