OL,4,Cof thousands of pounds because of
OL,5,Croadworks
OL,7,FOne business owner, David Hogben, has
OL,8,Fsold and restored pianos for the last
OL,9,F32 years, but from September, his shop
OL,10,Fwill close.
OL,12,FSince the roadworks, he has noticed a
OL,13,Fsharp fall in the number of sales that
OL,14,Fcame from people passing by the shop
OL,15,Fand is struggling to sell the stock.
OL,17,FNetwork Rail announced a #850,000
OL,18,Fsupport scheme, but David has been
OL,19,Ftold he does not qualify.
