OL,7,FMr Hogben has concerns because his
OL,8,Fform was filled in by Network Rail,
OL,9,Fand it says he could run his business
OL,10,Ffrom home and is not impacted by
OL,11,Fpassing trade.
OL,13,FDavid Hogben said: "When Network Rail
OL,14,Fmake the decision as to whether a
OL,15,Fbusiness is eligible or not.
OL,17,F"They actually send you this form, and
OL,18,Fthey actually fill in the answers for
OL,19,Fyou.
