OL,3,CBusinesses say they've lost hundreds
OL,4,Cof thousands of pounds because of
OL,5,Croadworks
OL,7,F"Now I mean this is surely nuts,
OL,8,Fbecause instead of asking the business
OL,9,Fin question, what kind of trade do you
OL,10,Fhave, where do you get your trade
OL,11,Ffrom, do you rely on the premises in
OL,12,Forder to survive.
OL,14,F"We are not having the chance to
OL,15,Fanswer that because they have filled
OL,16,Fin the answers already.
OL,18,F"September is now irrevocable, and
OL,19,Fthat's when we are having to move to
OL,20,Fmuch smaller premises, and sales at
OL,21,Fthat point will cease completely."
