OL,7,FThe bridge will now open next August,
OL,8,Falmost two years late. It's delayed
OL,9,Fbecause of issues with a sewer and
OL,10,Fproblems with a bridge arch.
OL,12,FA spokesperson from Network Rail said:
OL,13,F"We have followed the eligibility
OL,14,Fcriteria as set out with the
OL,15,FDepartment for Transport and HM
OL,16,FTreasury when the allocation of
OL,17,Fgoodwill payments to businesses
OL,18,Faffected by the ongoing delayed scheme
OL,19,Fat Botley Road was announced last
OL,20,Fmonth.
